1. Config all dependency needed in project
   - JPA
   - MySQL Driver
   - Web
   - Validation
   - starter-mail (Sending emails)
   - lombok
   - security (Authentication & authorization)
   - devtool
   - jjwt, jjwt-impl, jjwt-jackson (JWT token generation & validation)
   - stripe-java (Stripe payment integration)
   - razorpay-java (Razorpay payment integration)

2. For Authorization and authentication config
   - SecurityConfig (to make our config for security)
   - JwtValidator (for verify and validate the jwt)
   - JwtProvider (for generating jwt token)
   - JwtConstant (for constant variable used in jwt)
   - User (entity) , UserRole (enum define roles) & userRepository (to access user data form DataBase)
   - CustomUserDetails (for loading user by it email)

   - AuthService & AuthServiceImpl
   - UserDto, LoginRequest, SigninRequest, AuthResponse, ErrorResponse, UserMapper
   - UserException & GlobalExceptionHandler
   - AuthController

2.1 Users and docs (doc is optional)
   - UserService & UserServiceImpl
   - UserController
   - SwaggerConfig & OpenApiConstants (api doc but can config anytime also dependency needed)

2.2 Store
   - Store , StoreContact, StoreDto, StoreStatus, StoreMapper, StoreRepository
   - StoreService & StoreServiceImpl & StoreController
   - StoreException, UserException, JwtAuthEntryPoint (custom exception [optional])
   - APIResponse [optional]

2.3 Product and categories
   - product, productDto, productRepository, productMapper
   - productService & productServiceImpl & productController
   - category, categoryDTO, categoryRepository, categoryMapper
   - categoryService & categoryServiceImpl & categoryController
   - productException & productExceptionHandler,  categoryException & categoryExceptionHandler